Package hxasjc.utilstuff.util

Class TypeCheck

java.lang.Object
hxasjc.utilstuff.util.TypeCheck
public class TypeCheck extends Object
Debugging class used to find the type of a given variable.
All Methods return a TypeCheck.TypeCheckResult object
